#ingredients
- potato
- salt
- vinegar
- egg yolk
- olive oil

#preparation
- peel and dice potato
- boil them for 20 mins
- drain the water
- while it is still hot, add salt and vinegar
- let it cool down
- while the potato is cooled down, prepare the mayo by mixing egg yolk, oil, and vinegar
- after the potato is cooled down, mix it with the mayo
- enjoy!